        {
            "title": "東方海外首季航線收入按年降7.6%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">東方海外(00316)公布今年首季營運數字，期內航線收入21.38億美元，較去年同期減少7.6%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：東方海外官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250313_FI_source-web_00316-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：東方海外官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250313_FI_source-web_00316-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：東方海外官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">季度總載貨量則上升1.7%，運載力也升4.3%。整體運載率較2025年同期下降2.1%；每個標準箱的整體平均航線收入，則較去年同期減少9.1%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">以航線劃分，首季以亞洲區內/澳亞航線收入表現較佳，按年微升0.7%，增至7.49億美元；太平洋航線收入跌幅最大，按年降16.8%，跌至7.45億美元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15857287-%e6%9d%b1%e6%96%b9%e6%b5%b7%e5%a4%96%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e8%88%aa%e7%b7%9a%e6%94%b6%e5%85%a5%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e9%99%8d7-6",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240104_FI_source-web_00316.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-10 16:46:30",
